{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"283q","heading":"Eureka prize competitions","label":"283q Eureka prize competitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch6A/schIII/ptA","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs283q","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextSection 2032, referred to in subsec. (b)(2), means .section 2032 of Pub. L. 114–255","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the 21st Century Cures Act, and not as part of the Public Health Service Act which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs283q%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs283q%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Identifying and funding areas of biomedical science that could realize significant advancements through a prize competition.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs283q%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s283q/a/2/A","parentIdentifie